Committee Report: Favorable
Senate action: Adopted
Read second time: February 20, 2026
CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Notation of Veteran Status – Public Profiles
3 FOR the purpose of authorizing the Department of the Environment, the Department of
4 General Services, and units in the Maryland Department of Labor to include a
5 notation on certain public profiles indicating that an individual is a veteran; and
6 generally relating to the notation of veteran status on public profiles.
7 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
8 Article – Business Regulation
9 Section 2.5–103
10 Annotated Code of Maryland
11 (2024 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
12 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
13 Article – Environment
14 Section 1–206
15 Annotated Code of Maryland
16 (2013 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
17 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
18 Article – Health Occupations
19 Section 1–707
20 Annotated Code of Maryland
21 (2021 Replacement Volume and 2025 Supplement)
